    "description": "Night Fright 是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏：</h2>体验一位父亲在疯狂驱使下悲惨地杀死女儿的故事。在阴冷、充满气氛的房子里，您会体验到他日渐衰败的精神状态。随着他越来越陷入自己的噩梦，他必须面对自己行为的毁灭性后果，从而带来令人不安的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>探索房子并寻找钥匙、打火机、VHS 录像带等关键物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/aed44be09a06a62c126d4973b2c71f91.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>随着您进一步前进，您会遇到令人不安的超自然活动。调查它们，但要小心，因为您无法抵御那些躲在阴影中的人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您需要解决散布在各处的谜题才能取得进一步的进展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>死亡在某些时候可能是不可避免的，但要尽量避免被抓住。",
